These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, lawyer, police-officer
1. the lawyer is on the far left##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | lawyer | police-officer | software-developer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, scientist, security-guard
1. the security-guard is on the far right##1
2. the designer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | designer | scientist | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, woodworking, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | cooking | woodworking | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
