1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |

