.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, airplane
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | airplane | jet-ski | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, documentary, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | scientific | documentary |

 #################################

 
